1 0 0 1 56 740 Tm
(GOVERNMENT OF THE PUNJAB) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 724 Tm
(LOCAL GOVERNMENT AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT DEPARTMENT) Tj
/F1 6 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 708 Tm
() Tj
/F1 11 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 692 Tm
(CIRCULAR NO: LGCD-BR-2017-R12) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 676 Tm
(SUBJECT: Procedure for Delayed Birth Registration at Union Council) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 660 Tm
(Level) Tj
/F1 6 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 644 Tm
() Tj
/F1 11 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 628 Tm
(1. PURPOSE) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 612 Tm
(This circular prescribes the documents required and the approving authority for delayed) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 596 Tm
(birth registration \(LBR\) applications submitted through the Union Council Secretary.) Tj
/F1 6 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 580 Tm
() Tj
/F1 11 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 564 Tm
(2. REQUIRED DOCUMENTS FOR DELAYED BIRTH REGISTRATION) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 548 Tm
(For children aged 1 to 7 years, the applicant must submit Form A along with the parents CNIC) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 532 Tm
(copies, a hospital or Lady Health Worker certificate if available, and an affidavit) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 516 Tm
(confirming the date of birth. For children over 7 years of age, an additional affidavit from) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 500 Tm
(two witnesses and a school certificate, if the child is enrolled, are required along with) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 484 Tm
(Form A.) Tj
/F1 6 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 468 Tm
() Tj
/F1 11 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 452 Tm
(3. APPROVING AUTHORITY) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 436 Tm
(The Assistant Director Local Government \(ADLG\) of the concerned Tehsil is the approving) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 420 Tm
(authority for all delayed birth registration cases forwarded by the Secretary Union Council.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 404 Tm
(No delayed registration certificate shall be issued without the ADLG written approval) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 388 Tm
(recorded on Form A.) Tj
/F1 6 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 372 Tm
() Tj
/F1 11 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 356 Tm
(4. PROCESSING TIMELINE) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 340 Tm
(The Secretary Union Council must forward every delayed birth registration application to the) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 324 Tm
(ADLG within seven working days of receipt. The ADLG must record a decision, approval or) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 308 Tm
(rejection, within fourteen working days of receiving the forwarded application.) Tj
/F1 6 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 292 Tm
() Tj
/F1 11 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 276 Tm
(5. NIKAH REGISTRATION CROSS REFERENCE) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 260 Tm
(Nikah registration is a separate process governed by the Muslim Family Laws Ordinance 1961) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 244 Tm
(and is not covered under this circular. Secretaries should refer married applicants above 18) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 228 Tm
(years of age to the Nikah Registrar for that Union Council.) Tj
/F1 6 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 212 Tm
() Tj
/F1 11 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 196 Tm
(6. COMPLIANCE) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 180 Tm
(All Secretary Union Councils and ADLGs are directed to acknowledge receipt of this circular) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 164 Tm
(through the UC Governance Platform Knowledge Centre within seven days of publication.) Tj
/F1 6 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 148 Tm
() Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 132 Tm
(Issued by order of the Secretary, Local Government and Community Development Department,) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 116 Tm
(Government of the Punjab.) Tj
ET
